OL,3,CEpsom rape investigation closed as
OL,4,Cpolice say 'no offence took place'
OL,6,FAn investigation into an alleged rape
OL,7,Foutside a church in Epsom has been
OL,8,Fclosed after police said they were
OL,9,F"confident there was no offence".
OL,11,FSurrey Police said on Thursday that
OL,12,Ffollowing a "thorough investigation",
OL,13,Fit became clear that the woman in her
OL,14,F20s suffered an accidental head injury
OL,15,Ffollowing a night out, leading her to
OL,16,Fmake a confused report.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
