CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1776996209
OL,3,CEpsom rape investigation closed as
OL,4,Cpolice say 'no offence took place'
OL,6,FA spokesperson added: "The woman
OL,7,Finvolved has given us permission to
OL,8,Fshare this information and she
OL,9,Fcontinues to be supported by the
OL,10,Frelevant services."
OL,12,FThe force received a report on
OL,13,FSaturday, April 11, that a woman had
OL,14,Fbeen raped near a church in the early
OL,15,Fhours of the morning after leaving
OL,16,FLabyrinth nightclub in the town.
OL,18,FThe alleged incident led to widespread
OL,19,Fpublic disorder and unrest after
OL,20,Fpolice did not release the ethnicity
OL,21,Fof any suspects.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
