CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1776996209
OL,3,CEpsom rape investigation closed as
OL,4,Cpolice say 'no offence took place'
OL,6,F"We are now confident that there was
OL,7,Fno offence, and there were no
OL,8,Fsuspects."
OL,10,FThe force said its detectives carried
OL,11,Fout an "extensive examination" of CCTV
OL,12,Ffootage of the woman's movements, as
OL,13,Fwell as house-to-house inquiries,
OL,14,Finterviews with witnesses, and
OL,15,Fforensic tests.
OL,17,F"To be clear, we take every report of
OL,18,Fsexual offending seriously, and any
OL,19,Fsuch report is treated with
OL,20,Fsensitivity," the force added in its
OL,21,Fstatement.
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@JO]sD@HOUsD@^O]yD@AOU|D@MO]
