OL,3,CEpsom rape investigation closed as
OL,4,Cpolice say 'no offence took place'
OL,6,F"To do this, it is imperative that the
OL,7,Fappropriate time is allowed to
OL,8,Fcomplete a thorough investigation and
OL,9,Fsupport is given to the complainant to
OL,10,Fprogress inquiries at their own pace.
OL,12,F"This limits what information we are
OL,13,Fable to release publicly," the force
OL,14,Fsaid.
OL,16,FClashes between police and protesters
OL,17,Fon Monday saw eggs and beer cans
OL,18,Fthrown at officers, with Surrey Police
OL,19,Fand Crime Commissioner Lisa Townsend
OL,20,Fcondemning the actions as "shameful".
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUuD@ZO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
