OL,3,CEpsom rape investigation closed as
OL,4,Cpolice say 'no offence took place'
OL,6,FShe added that some of those involved
OL,7,Fin the unrest had travelled from
OL,8,Felsewhere to cause trouble, and warned
OL,9,Fthem to stay away.
OL,11,F"I am a firm believer in people's
OL,12,Fright to lawful protest, but sadly,
OL,13,Fsome of those present in Epsom
OL,14,Fyesterday stepped way beyond that line
OL,15,Fand the type of behaviour we witnessed
OL,16,Fwill not be tolerated," she said.
OL,26,@sD@AOUxD@WO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
