PN,31407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1776996209
OL,3,CEpsom rape investigation closed as
OL,4,Cpolice say 'no offence took place'
OL,6,F"The reality is that a number of those
OL,7,Fin Epsom last night were not local and
OL,8,Fhave come into the town from
OL,9,Felsewhere, clearly with their own
OL,10,Fagenda.
OL,12,F"My message to those intent on
OL,13,Fstirring up trouble under the guise of
OL,14,Flegitimate protest is: stay away from
OL,15,FEpsom.
OL,17,F"If you involve yourself in disorder,
OL,18,Fthe police will take robust action and
OL,19,FI expect you to face the full force of
OL,20,Fthe law."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUyD@AOU|D@IO]
