OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1776996209
OL,3,CEpsom rape investigation closed as
OL,4,Cpolice say 'no offence took place'
OL,6,FFour people were arrested after the
OL,7,Fitems were thrown at police in riot
OL,8,Fgear on Monday evening, and one man
OL,9,Fappeared to try to climb on top of a
OL,10,Fpolice van.
OL,12,FIt was the second protest in the town
OL,13,Ffollowing the rape allegation.
OL,15,FOn April 15, footage posted on social
OL,16,Fmedia showed a large crowd of
OL,17,Fprotesters had congregated in the town
OL,18,Fcentre.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/9
