OL,6,FDozens of police officers could be
OL,7,Fseen wearing helmets and holding
OL,8,Fshields, with objects appearing to
OL,9,Fhave been thrown at them.
OL,11,FThe protest was promoted online by
OL,12,FDanny Tommo, a former associate of
OL,13,Fright-wing activist Tommy Robinson.
